summary: Changes your race benefits, but not looks, height, weight, or anything affected by height. Only usable at level 1 with initial skills, spells, and items.
descriptionHtml:
I spent an hour or so meticulously compiling these for personal reasons, and I figured I might as well upload them. Not sure many people would find a use for them, though.

Changes your race benefits, but not looks, height, weight, or anything affected by height. Only usable at level 1 with initial skills, spells, and items.

Make sure you follow that last instruction. Also, you may have a preference to rename the files to make loading them via the console easier.

Instructions: load console, and use the [bat \"filename.txt\"] command.
author: Someone
